abstract.p:
Method comprising the steps of:

determining an oxygen concentration deviation between an oxygen concentration setpoint and an estimated oxygen concentration that is estimated from actual cylinder pressure;

determining a boost pressure deviation between a boost pressure setpoint and an actual boost pressure;

producing a boost pressure control output in response to the boost pressure deviation; and

producing an oxygen concentration control output in response to the oxygen concentration deviation and the boost pressure control output.

Method comprising the steps of: 
determining an oxygen concentration deviation between an oxygen concentration setpoint and an estimated oxygen concentration that is estimated from actual cylinder pressure; 
determining a boost pressure deviation between a boost pressure setpoint and an actual boost pressure; 
producing a boost pressure control output in response to the boost pressure deviation; and 
producing an oxygen concentration control output in response to the oxygen concentration deviation and the boost pressure control output.

